window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>OK, Reg. You’re a bouncer who’s barely eking out a meager existence in the decaying Wilds outside Detroit. So a little job tracking the Eddies on their patrols seems like easy money. Well, think again, Reg. Because a riot’s about to happen… and you’re going to be the cause…</p><p>This story was originally published in the Hugo Award-nominated <i>METAtropolis</i>. </p>"; 
